Class StatisticsApp

  • java.lang.Object
    • WeatherObserver
      • StatisticsApp

  • public class StatisticsApp
extends WeatherObserver
    A weather statistics app calculates the minimum, maximum, and average temperature read so far from its subscribed weather station, if any.
